cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with 3D shape recovery from a single image using deep neural networks. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The paper proposes a novel approach using Gaussian mixture models, which involves training the network using two loss functions. This suggests that the paper may also fall under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE).
